{"type":null,"faqId":34775,"title":" How do I enable a screen lock that must be unlocked using a pattern?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>Touch </span><span class=\"s2\">Settings</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s2\">Security</span><span> &lt; </span><span class=\"s2\">Screen lock</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s2\">Pattern</span><span>. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110879\" style=\"width:1.3986111in;height:2.4854167in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110880\" style=\"width:1.3875in;height:2.4756944in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110881\" style=\"width:1.40625in;height:2.4826388in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>On the </span><span class=\"s2\">Choose your pattern</span><span> screen, draw your pattern by connecting dots and touch </span><span class=\"s2\">Continue</span><span>. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>Draw the pattern again to verify it. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>When you press the power key to light up the screen or power on your phone, you need to draw the pattern to unlock. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110882\" style=\"width:1.5819445in;height:2.8125in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110883\" style=\"width:1.3986111in;height:2.4819446in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":244,"languageName":"mm","faqCode":"9515","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436871812000,"seriesProductName":"H30-L02","visitedTimes":1,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"HONOR 3C LTE (H30-L02)","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}